fields.value: Stata Do Files for the paper, "META-ANALYSIS AND PUBLICATION BIAS: HOW WELL DOES THE FAT-PET-PEESE PROCEDURE WORK?"

dsDescriptionValue.value:
The Stata do files in this dataset enable the user to replicate TABLES 2, 3, 4 and 6. (The code for TABLES 8-11 are in R and can be found here: https://dataverse.harvard.edu/dataset.xhtml?persistentId=doi:10.7910/DVN/C4KIYK). 

The do files are in two parts. The "A" program should be run first before running the "B" program.  Running times for each program are given at the top of the B programs.
